Get everyone on Ryver. Email me your preferred mail.

Install Node.js
https://nodejs.org/en/download/
If you are on Linux (especially Ubuntu) then be careful not to install an old version. Above version 7.6 is preferable.

Sucess criteria 1: type node --version in your terminal 
Sucess criteria 2: type npm in your terminal and see a list of options and commands.

For querying our APIs:
https://www.getpostman.com/

Install the helpful extension magicss if you are using Chrome. It's ok if you are using a different browser. Skip this step then.
https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/live-editor-for-css-less/ifhikkcafabcgolfjegfcgloomalapol?hl=en

Install Vs Code. Which will be our text editor:
https://code.visualstudio.com/download